title: Wilco's Jeff Tweedy & The 8G Band's Eli Janney
description:
Jeff Tweedy (Wilco, Uncle Tupelo) sits down with Eli Janney (The 8G Band, Girls Against Boys) at the Late Night offices to discuss their careers in music.
